==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pasty
<hw>Pas"ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like paste, as in
color, softness, stickness.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>pasty</xex>
complexion.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>G. Eliot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

